Epidemiology
Source of the outbreak(s) or origin of infection: unknown or inconclusive

Control measures
Measures applied: stamping out; quarantine; movement control inside the country; screening; zoning; no vaccination; no treatment of affected animals
Measures to be applied: vaccination in response to the outbreak(s); disinfection of infected premises/establishment(s)

Diagnostic test results
Laboratory name and type: Kimron Veterinary Institute, Avian Diseases Laboratory (national laboratory)
Species / Test / Test date / Result
Birds / real-time PCR / 26 Mar 2015 / Positive

